&quot;I believe you would Livia.  You seem like one that wouldn't break her word.&quot;  The rest... she decided to send through mindspeech.  She wasn't sure about how the other two would react to her statement and she didn't want to offend anyone.. it wasn't like her.. so she looked to Livia with a smile.<br>
